name: A Song of Hex and Jynx - #3 A Witch is Not A God
description: Ilyon, one of the witch, found a dead moth in a forest. She felt sad as she fell in love with the beauty of its wings, even though it was broken and imperfect. Hidden from her sisters, she casted a forbidden art of resurrection so the moth could be alive again. “What is wrong with helping a beautiful creature to live again?” She thought. She smiled as she saw the moth flew away from her hand, ignoring the rule her mother taught her; that a witch is not a god.
